---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Shopify Accessibility Tools — Moved to Appnary"
  description="AmazingPlugins now focuses on WooCommerce. Our Shopify accessibility tools and content have moved to appnary.com."
>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 5rem;">
    <div class="wrap" style="max-width: 680px;">
      <div class="chip" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <span class="chip-dot"></span>
        <span>Update</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); margin-bottom: 24px;">
        Shopify tools have <em>moved</em>.
      </h1>
      <p class="lede" style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 40px;">
        AmazingPlugins now focuses entirely on WooCommerce. All our Shopify accessibility
        tools, apps, and expertise have moved to <strong>appnary.com</strong> — our dedicated
        Shopify agency.
      </p>

      <a href="https://appnary.com" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Visit appnary.com for Shopify
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" width="14" height="14"><path d="M3 8h10m-4-4 4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap" style="max-width: 680px;">
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        What happened?
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 32px;">
        We built our first accessibility tools for Shopify stores. As we grew, we realised
        WooCommerce merchants needed the same level of care — so we shifted our main focus.
        The Shopify side of the business is now run by <strong>appnary.com</strong>, who
        handle Shopify accessibility, app development, and compliance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        What about the old blog posts?
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 8px;">
        All our previous Shopify articles have been moved. You can find them — and much more
        Shopify-specific content — at appnary.com.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65;">
        If you are looking for WooCommerce accessibility help, you are in the right place.
        Browse our <a href="/plugins/">plugins</a> or <a href="/blog/">blog</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--cream-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--ink-3);
  }
  .chip-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--coral);
  }
</style>
